<div><head>常璩蜀李書</head>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a" ed="CHANT" n="001-1a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.2">武皇帝諱雄，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.3">字仲儁，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.4">始祖第三子。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.5">身長八尺三寸，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.6">美容貌，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.7">相工相之曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.8">「北君將貴。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.9">其相有四：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.10">目如重雲、鼻如龜龍、口如方器、耳如相望。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.11">法為貴人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.12">位必過三公。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.13">不疑也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.14">帝每周旋鄉里，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.15">有識者皆器量之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.16">有劉化者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.17">道術士也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.18">太康中，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.19">每語鄉里曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.20">「李仲儁有大貴之表，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.21">終為人主也。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-1a.22">《御覽》三百六十、又二百六十六。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a" ed="CHANT" n="001-2a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.2">武帝諱雄，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.3">始祖第三子。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.4">始祖后方娠，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.5">夢隻蛇自門升天，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.6">一蛇中斷。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.7">及生，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.8">后常言子若成人，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.9">必有先亡者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.10">有大貴者。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.11">後果李蕩早卒，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.12">李雄王蜀。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-2a.13">同上三百九十八。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-3a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-3a" ed="CHANT" n="001-3a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-3a.2">武皇帝雄泰武三年，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-3a.3">白烏赤足來翔。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-3a.4">帝以問范賢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-3a.5">賢曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-3a.6">「烏有反哺之義，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-3a.7">必有遠人懷惠而來。」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-3a.8">果關中流民請降。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-3a.9">《類聚》九十二。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-3a.10">按：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-3a.11">此引作《蜀李雄書》。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a" ed="CHANT" n="001-4a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.2">蜀才姓范，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.3">名長生，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.4">一名賢，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.5">隱居青城山，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.6">自號蜀才。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.7">李雄以為丞相。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.8">《釋文序》注解傳述人注。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.9">按《顏氏家訓‧書證篇》。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.10">引《李蜀書》，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.11">一名《漢之書》，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.12">云姓范，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.13">名長生，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-4a.14">自號蜀才。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a" ed="CHANT" n="001-5a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.2">賈夷字景叔，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.3">梓潼人也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.4">太始初，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.5">內移河東，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.6">少仕晉臺，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.7">為倉部令史。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.8">懷帝時，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.9">為安富令。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.10">中原喪亂，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.11">玉衡七年歸國。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.12">武帝素聞夷名，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.13">重之，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.14">皇子雅生，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.15">因名賈夷。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-5a.16">《御覽》三百六十二。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.1"><pb xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a" ed="CHANT" n="001-6a"/><lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.2">武帝諸將進金銀，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.3">或以得官者，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.4">楊襃諫曰：<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.5">「陛下為天下主，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.6">何得以官賣金耶！」<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.7">帝謝之。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.8">《御覽》三百十一。<lb/></seg>
</p>
<p>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.9">哀帝即位，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.10">有白氣二道帶天，<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.11">望氣者言宮中有伏兵。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.12">果為邛都公所害也。<lb/></seg>
<seg xml:id="CH2c1301_CHANT_001-6a.13">《御覽》八百七十七。<lb/></seg>
</p>
</div>
